{"tid":693384,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我同我老公生左個黃皮膚bb女（突發）","createTime":"2018-06-07T12:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T12:19:22.000Z","uid":80567,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea810bfdfb6fea000bb40ddfee68a98f49eacdad","tid":693384,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:09:03.000Z","msg":"講少少背景先<br />\n我同我老公拍左拖兩年之後結婚<br />\n依家都岩岩慶祝左三週年結婚紀念日<br />\n佢就廿五歲<br />\n我就廿二歲<br />\n<br />\n上星期我地生左個女，有開心有唔開心既地方<br />\n因為我地一直都同醫生講想知男定女，老婆都話好，自己就想要女多啲<br />\n但生左出黎係個黃皮膚既bb女<br />\n當然我地係正常非洲人啦<br />\n<br />\n醫生就話唔知幾多百萬份之一會發生喱啲事<br />\n<br />\n我依家唔知驗唔驗dna好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 信我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驗dna<br />\ncomment 俾返個仔人"},{"pid":"895b92941f2444a50096c6ded3c8650b78df7281","tid":693384,"uid":130044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"你老婆定老公呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa0b5dc49bd6c5f25c3db9b0460101dd50d4e1a","tid":693384,"uid":179938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:13:42.000Z","msg":"非洲你住晒?<br />\n利申: 長洲"},{"pid":"9143eb25ac15972c92f6dc391a1ebd32ce67dcf8","tid":693384,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"895b92941f2444a50096c6ded3c8650b78df7281","tid":693384,"uid":130044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"你老婆定老公呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:15:09.000Z","msg":"左膠話要多元成家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8785cac1bde52ac4be03e97b191231235eec8c","tid":693384,"uid":165936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:15:32.000Z","msg":"好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n100分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.